der, YWTFL | Empowering Children, Youth & Communities Through Tech & Purpose\\n\\n1mo • \\n\\n🚀 𝗜 𝗷𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝗳𝗼𝘂𝗻𝗱 𝗮 𝗚𝗢𝗟𝗗 𝗠𝗜𝗡𝗘 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗗𝗲𝘃𝗢𝗽𝘀 𝗘𝗻𝗴𝗶𝗻𝗲𝗲𝗿𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟲!\\nIf you are an aspiring DevOps Engineer or looking to level up your cloud game this year, you need to see this.\\n\\nThe landscape is shifting fast - Kubernetes is standard, AI is integrating into workflows, and platform engineering is taking off.\\nIf you're struggling to build your DevOps portfolio, I just discovered an incredible GitHub repository with 30+ hands-on DevOps projects (beginner to advanced).\\n\\nThis repo covers: \\n✅ Docker & Kubernetes \\n✅ CI/CD Pipelines \\n✅ Terraform & IaC\\n✅ AWS, Azure & GCP\\n✅ Monitoring & Logging \\n✅ Microservices Architecture\\nPerfect for: \\n🔹 Building your portfolio \\n🔹 Interview preparation \\n🔹 Hands-on learning \\n🔹 Real-world practice\\nI found this super helpful and wanted to share it with the community!\\n\\nHere's the link: https://lnkd.in/ejKbMKg3\\n\\nThis repo has 30+ hands-on projects covering Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD, Terraform, and more.\\n\\nReshare to help your network grow\\nLet's learn and grow together! 💪\\n\\nCredit: @DevCloud Ninjas\\n\\nFollow Kareen A. for insights in DevOps and Cloud\\n\\n#DevOps #CloudComputing #Kubernetes #Docker #TechCommunity\\n#LearningTogether\\n… more\\n\\nMohannad Elewaily and 675 others reacted\\nMohannad Elewaily and 675 others\\n\\n32 comments\\n32 comments\\n\\n•\\n\\n177 reposts\\n177 reposts\\n\\nLike\\nComment\\nRepost\\nSend\\n\\nMohannad Elewaily reposted this\\n\\nSherry Zaky\\n\\n \\n • 2nd\\n\\nProblem Manager at Orange Business Services | Certified Scrum Master (CSM®)
